body: "Self-hosting requirements:\n- The release tracker must contain closed items with useful titles, types, release metadata, and verification evidence.\n- The package CLI should read pm list-all --json from this workspace.\n- CHANGELOG.md should be updated in prepend mode so previous release history is preserved where headings do not conflict.\n- Changelog check should pass after regeneration."
